 press the rematch button....there is no rematch. The Spirit doesn't even show up on the map before I leave and come back. Or maybe it's just made to be this way? In any case, this button didn't work for me :/Even with all these cons, this is a very good game to play, if you just want to play a game. For me, this is probably gonna be the game I play again to take a break of the others I have played too much."
