76561198005260241,Not Recommended,266490,16246113,"Posted: 7 June, 2015",all,Perfect Hair,"So I haven't given this game a full playthrough yet, but if this game does not change too much from the first two sections of the main story (and sources indicate that it doesn't), then I don't believe that I'll need to in order to justify this review. I bought this game based off positive review and what seemed to be a game with rather pretty game design from the trailers. And sure, the game is rather gorgeous on most occasions. What really bothers me, however, is that all the overworld design and assets ultimately do not play a huge role in what becomes the main goal, so there is no real incentive to explore the world at large. There are mini-quests you are able to undertake, but they are simple ""just find x in this area"" collection quests. Movement is alright, but there is no jumping or running, and speed boosts and special potions in this game seem kind of rough around the edges, ultimately not fitting in with the rest of the game design.To save the spoilers, albeit the story is rather sparse and easy anyhow, you play as a graduate botanist student where the main goal of the gameplay is to jump on the backs of spirits, and by using the keys (or the xyba buttons of an xbox controller) you must grab a special flower off the spirits for your report. It's simple, cheesy at times, and vaguely child-friendly. There are constant innuendos, so I guess it's supposed to be a game for everyone, but the simplicity of the game mechanics and the lack of content reveals the game to be a simple collection time-waster for a much younger age group. And although I would recommend this game for a younger audience, this game may never challenge anyone older than 8 years old.If you are someone who is looking for a cute puzzle platformer like I was, then do not buy this game. I'd recommend that people keep an eye on this studio, however, because it seems like they have all of the assets to make a great game, but did not deliver on anything substantial this go around."
